      • isValidList

        public static boolean isValidList(String listName)
        Check if the provided list name is a valid list name registered in the GNS as a field of the proxy group
        Parameters:
        listName - the list name to check
        Returns:
        true if the name is valid (backed by a field of the same name in the GNS)
